Installation
------------
In the php.ini file:
- make sure that always_populate_raw_post_data = On

Copy openquestion.ini_INSTALL to openquestion.ini and edit it to reflect your setup

Copy openquestion.wsdl_INSTALL to openquestion.wsdl and modify
the location of the service (at the end of the file)

Consider copying robots.txt_INSTALL to robots.txt
